    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a MarkupSafe Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>MarkupSafe</application> is a <application>Python</application>
module that implements a XML/HTML/XHTML Markup safe string.
      </para>

      <note revision="systemd">
        <para>
          <application>MarkupSafe</application> was installed in LFS.  The instruction
is only kept here for SysV revision.
        </para>
      </note>

      &lfs113_checked;

